Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:20.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition \N- in which a winner will get the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flare-Flare Fruit as the prize \N- and won the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zoro and Kin'emon finally \Ngot to see Luffy again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand called the others through the Transponder Snails{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and checked how everybody was doing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently with the King Riku Army,\Nan anti-Doflamingo coalition in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An army?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Of Little People.\N--{\i1}Little People?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the people here are looking to\Ntake down Doflamingo this very day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is willing to sacrifice his life\Nto destroy this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky, stop the army!\N--{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brave, little army...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...let them down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}'s gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Franky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's going on?! The town is...\N--It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tra-guy! Why are you with Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've pushed it too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Two Great Rivals Meet Each Other!\NStraw Hat and Heavenly Demon!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I heard some explosions and gunshots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhat happened to Tra-guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say something, Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a Warlord and a pirate - Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was behind the false report of\Nmy abdication from the throne this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Withdraws from the Seven Warlords"?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Why did you resign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a reason, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying to drag me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry!\NI've just gotten rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it what it was all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he almost messed Dressrosa up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you shoot Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your damn business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law was originally my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility for dealing with him\Nfalls to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin, retrieve Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral-{\i1}dono{\i0},\NPirate Hunter is in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Talk to us! What's going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}'s got shot in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter and Foxfire Kin'emon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a child who looked like \NMomonosuke on the ship earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to him!\NWe won't let him take Momo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you're so strong!\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not tell you that\Nfor the sake of both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this heaviness?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can he create this much force?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to Zoro, Kin'emon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0} has just vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... It's Sea Prism Stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kin'emon-san?! Are you okay?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no, don't tell me you're dead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can launch a sword attack from \Na distance? That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the civilians to evacuate\Nas far as possible from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the blind old \Ngambler was a Navy admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is an admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear you, Kin'emon-san!\NOh, good! You're alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people were nice to me\Nso it feels like I'm repaying you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for kindness with ingratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is full of ironies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NA man who stands by Doflamingo is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...N...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Navy admiral!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Navy admiral is there in Dressrosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, Doflamingo has\Nthe Navy on his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there are hundreds of enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of the number!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NJust one admiral is already a big problem to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}! Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk at the palace, Fujitora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cooperate with me,\NI'll let you catch those brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will listen to what you have to say,\NHeavenly Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will decide what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All civilians are evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know who we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kin'emon!\NLaw-{\i1}dono{\i0} has been abducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Look for the exit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna wait for you\Nby running around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We gotta hurry!\NTra-guy said something after being shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Brook and the others!\NWhat happened now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-W-We...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They've found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pirate ship is here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ship! Ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the ship of one of the Four Emperors\Ndoing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its figurehead is singing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ship! Ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?! Big Mom's ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're gonna die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NIs Big Mom on board?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy! Run with us while talking!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see those two that we \Nmet on the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! I see Caesar! Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have him with them\Nas we thought-{\i1}bon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sink their ship\Nand recover just Caesar-{\i1}soir{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom?! That's what I'm concerned about!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! You shouldn't have \Npicked a fight with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seems like they're here for Caesar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they want from him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants you, you mad scientist!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they come to rescue you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get caught by Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NBecause I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...swindled research funds from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip the details! They're gonna kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once they catch me and confirm \Nthat I've been fooling them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you live or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let anyone take \Nyou anyway so shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna shoot at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, take the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're rolling away from Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you shake them off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Brook! Keep trying!\N--Yes, I'll keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, don't bring the Emperor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll throw the whole country out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and mess up the plan of Toy \NSoldier and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwhy is Caesar on the Sunny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal fell apart!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, why would Tra-guy \Nhave to go through it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law told us to take Caesar\Nto the next island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I think we shouldn't \Ngo back to Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to join them\Nand rescue Tra-guy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and help the Little People's army\Nwin the fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying this because I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three things that we and \NDoflamingo are scrambling for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The SMILE factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Momonosuke for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't destroyed the factory yet\Nso it's still in his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have the other two with us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:03.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tra-guy was sacrificing himself and fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto let these two get away from Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe, he also wanted to buy time\Nfor destroying the factory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went that far to save these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we go back and make it easier \Nfor Doflamingo to catch them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all his efforts will be ruined!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take Tra-guy back at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the name of the next island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nami!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brook!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You go ahead and sail for Zou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so... Roger that, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how about giving us permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Permission to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...launch a counterattack\Nagainst Big Mom's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already picked a fight with her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's too dangerous!\N--Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys!\NWe'll be waiting for you at Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on us to destroy the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He holds the key to all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna head for the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beat the hell out of Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
